Welcome

Note
Welcome to HeapNote. Here are some tips.
To add a new note, just type something in the field above and press Enter. If you type: #important, you will quickly add a label: 'important' to the new note.
We've created some tables for you - you can keep here your Notes, Schedule, and Tasks.To add a new table, click on the '+' button, to remove a tab, click Table->Remove.
To mark a note with a label, simply drag it here from the tree on the left hand side :)
You can quickly save selected text when browsing using HeapNote Extension for Chrome: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/lephjpbfkjbomhpnellaiddfemllekfh
